The paper deals with frequency permutation arrays, which are related to error correcting codes, and proposes two algorithms to compute the ball size of frequency permutations under Chebyshev distance. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Information Theory (cs.IT), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Computational Complexity (cs.CC), or Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
